4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science and Machine Learning course designed for beginners with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students learn essential skills in Python, SQL, and statistics, as well as how to create predictive models using advanced libraries. The program covers various algorithms and provides hands-on experience to tackle real-world challenges. Classes are conducted thrice weekly with a maximum of 12 students per class, ensuring personalized attention. Participants receive a recognized certificate upon completion. The course can be taken in either English or Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop